<promed@promedmail.org>
[From this item it seems that "clams, fish and soil" are suspected by the
Taiwanese investigators to be the toxin source. It is not clear whether
this conclusion was based upon bacteria isolates or demonstrated toxin.
Previous press items (see 20030101.0001) mentioned Cl. botulinum type C as
the causative agent. - Mod.AS]
